Make sure that you have Clang and LLVM 3.8.1 in your PATH.  E.g.,
if you have downloaded binaries for Ubuntu 14.04:

export PATH=${HOME}/clang+llvm-3.8.1-x86_64-linux-gnu-ubuntu-14.04/bin:${PATH}

